rows.label: qev086702_MSG0001
rows.name: Wow, what a great view of New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0002
rows.name: Huh? Tatsu not see city anywhere.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0003
rows.name: It's right in front of you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0004
rows.name: Tatsu enjoy rich imagination of friends, but this is silly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0005
rows.name: New LA not sitting inside little bowl.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0006
rows.name: Little bowl?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0007
rows.name: Hmm, I suppose you could see it that way...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0008
rows.name: Seeing it from the outside, it does look kinda small, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0009
rows.name:
Perhaps it's not that New LA looks small
so much as Mira is just massive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0010
rows.name:
Yeah... And space is even bigger. WAY bigger.
And Earth is so far away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0011
rows.name: I mean...it used to be.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0012
rows.name:
To think, humanity crossed that vast distance
with an entire city in tow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0013
rows.name: It's an amazing feat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0014
rows.name: Tatsu agree![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0015
rows.name: New LA is amazing place. All races living there agree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0016
rows.name:
Perhaps someday we'll be able to set sail together
aboard a new White Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0017
rows.name: To carry forth the bonds we forged on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0018
rows.name: Awww, it sounds so nice when you put it that way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0019
rows.name: But Elma, why did you want to come here right now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0020
rows.name: I stood here the day the White Whale crashed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0021
rows.name: It was the first spot I touched after leaving my Skell.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0022
rows.name: The sunset was so beautiful...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0023
rows.name:
Now that we've secured the Lifehold,
I wanted to come back and remember that day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0024
rows.name: Also, to think about what comes next.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0025
rows.name: And I wanted you all here with me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0027
rows.name: Everyone! Behind us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0028
rows.name: So it's you...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0029
rows.name: Elma?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0030
rows.name: This one's strong, Lin. You all need to run.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0031
rows.name: Then run with us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0032
rows.name: I can't. This is...personal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_JNK0010
rows.name: Assert

rows.label: qev086702_SEL0011
rows.name: Claim that you won't abandon her.

rows.label: qev086702_JNK0020
rows.name: Warn

rows.label: qev086702_SEL0021
rows.name: Say she's getting too emotional.

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0033
rows.name: Absolutely not. I told you, this thing is strong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0034
rows.name: What's going on, Elma?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0035
rows.name: No. This is a calm, rational order.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0036
rows.name: It sure doesn't sound rational! What's going on?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0037
rows.name: We made it all this way by fighting together![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0038
rows.name: I...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0039
rows.name: You're right. I'm sorry. Would you lend me a hand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0040
rows.name: Of course.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086702_MSG0041
rows.name: Leave it to Tatsu![ST:wait ]
